==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
Pinyin: sān k chǎnyè

===Etymology===
From the Japanese term "3K shigoto" ([[3K仕事]], "3K jobs"), which stands for '''k'''itsui ([[きつい]] difficult), '''k'''itanai ([[汚い]] dirty) and '''k'''iken ([[危険]] dangerous).

===Noun===
'''3K[[产业]]'''
#[[3D jobs]] (dirty, dangerous and difficult jobs)

===Alternate forms===
[[3K產業]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

